node.text: Who wants to experience an Italian summer at @eatalyflatiron & @eatalydowntown? 🥂🇮🇹🍝 From a scoop of housemade gelato or fresh pasta for a night in, to seasonal dishes at blooming rooftop Serra by Birreria, a refreshing Spritz at the piazza-inspired Il Patio di Eataly, & authentic Italian staples at La Pizza & La Pasta A Colori, there are so many ways to explore these two marketplaces. Check our link-in-bio for full details! #NYC #Partner

node.text: Art has taken over the streets of @meatpackingny 🎨🎶 'From A Place Of A Place' @artnoirco has popped up for the next 3 months featuring art & performances celebrating Black culture. The Meeting Point Gallery is open to the public 7 days a week and will feature a second gallery exhibition starting September 30. The next Visions in Motion performance will take place on October 2nd. Full details + see more at our link-in-bio. #NYbucketlist #Partner #Meatpacking

node.text:
Summer Dream Pass GIVEAWAY💦🎢🥳 To help you cool off in this August heat, we’re giving away a bundle from our friends at @AmericanDream: 4 tickets to DreamWorks Water Park, 4 tickets to Nickelodeon Universe & exclusive merch! 
To Enter: 1. Tag your friends and 2. Follow @AmericanDream
Explore American Dream this summer - with roller coaster thrills, the largest indoor wave pool, an indoor ski hill & more. Check our link-in-bio for full details & special pricing! #NYC #Partner -- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, will end on 11:59 EST 8/25. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms

node.text:
GIVEAWAY 🏙🎉 Who wants $500 to explore the vibrant @hudsonsquareproperties neighborhood? 

Enter To Win: Tag a friend you'd explore with & Follow @hudsonsquareproperties
(Winner will receive a $500 visa gift card to use for a day of exploring Hudson Square)

From a handful of art installations, urban spaces like Restorative Ground, restaurants, & of course the iconic Hudson River Park...There's no shortage of things to do this summer. See our stories + Link-In-Bio for the full guide @newyork_instagram  #Partner #HudsonSquare #NYC 
-- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, value $500, will end on 11:59 EST 8/12. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms
